manifests.contents:
[workspace]
members = ["egui_plot", "demo", "examples/*"]
resolver = "2"

[workspace.dependencies]
document-features = "0.2.10"
log = "0.4"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4"
web-sys = "0.3.70"

[workspace.dependencies.ahash]
version = "0.8.11"
features = ["no-rng", "std"]
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.eframe]
version = "0.32"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.egui]
version = "0.32"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.egui_kittest]
version = "0.32"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.egui_plot]
version = "0.0.1"
path = "egui_plot"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.emath]
version = "0.32"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.env_logger]
version = "0.11.6"
features = ["auto-color", "humantime"]
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.image]
version = "0.25"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]

[workspace.package]
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
rust-version = "1.85"

[patch.crates-io]

[profile.release]
opt-level = 2

[profile.release.package]

[profile.dev.package."*"]
opt-level = 2

[package]
name = "demo"
authors = ["Emil Ernerfeldt <emil.ernerfeldt@gmail.com>"]
include = ["../LICENSE-APACHE", "../LICENSE-MIT", "**/*.rs", "Cargo.toml"]
default-run = "demo"
publish = false

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.version]
workspace = true

[package.license]
workspace = true

[package.rust-version]
workspace = true

[dependencies.eframe]
workspace = true
features = ["default_fonts", "glow", "persistence"]

[dependencies.egui]
workspace = true

[dependencies.egui_kittest]
workspace = true

[dependencies.egui_plot]
workspace = true
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.log]
workspace = true

[dependencies.serde]
workspace = true
features = ["derive"]

[dev-dependencies.egui_kittest]
workspace = true
features = ["snapshot", "wgpu", "eframe"]

[target.'cfg(not(target_arch = "wasm32"))'.dependencies.env_logger]
workspace = true

[target.'cfg(not(target_arch = "wasm32"))'.dev-dependencies]

[target.'cfg(not(target_arch = "wasm32"))'.build-dependencies]

[target.'cfg(target_arch = "wasm32")'.dependencies.wasm-bindgen-futures]
workspace = true

[target.'cfg(target_arch = "wasm32")'.dependencies.web-sys]
workspace = true

[target.'cfg(target_arch = "wasm32")'.dev-dependencies]

[target.'cfg(target_arch = "wasm32")'.build-dependencies]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "demo"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/plot.rs"
name = "plot"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "demo"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "egui_plot"
authors = ["Emil Ernerfeldt <emil.ernerfeldt@gmail.com>", "Jan Haller <bromeon@gmail.com>", "Sven Niederberger <s-niederberger@outlook.com>"]
description = "Immediate mode plotting for the egui GUI library"
homepage = "https://github.com/emilk/egui_plot"
readme = "../README.md"
keywords = ["egui", "plot", "plotting"]
categories = ["visualization", "gui"]
repository = "https://github.com/emilk/egui_plot"
include = ["../LICENSE-APACHE", "../LICENSE-MIT", "**/*.rs", "Cargo.toml"]

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.version]
workspace = true

[package.license]
workspace = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true

[package.rust-version]
workspace = true

[dependencies.ahash]
workspace = true

[dependencies.document-features]
workspace = true
optional = true

[dependencies.egui]
workspace = true

[dependencies.emath]
workspace = true

[dependencies.serde]
workspace = true
optional = true

[features]
default = []
serde = ["dep:serde", "egui/serde"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "egui_plot"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "borrow_points"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Nicolas <bircni@icloud.com>"]
publish = false

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.license]
workspace = true

[package.rust-version]
workspace = true

[dependencies.eframe]
workspace = true
features = ["default"]

[dependencies.egui_plot]
workspace = true

[dependencies.env_logger]
workspace = true
features = ["auto-color", "humantime"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "borrow_points"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[package]
name = "custom_plot_manipulation"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Ygor Souza <ygor.souza@protonmail.com>"]
publish = false

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.license]
workspace = true

[package.rust-version]
workspace = true

[dependencies.eframe]
workspace = true
features = ["default"]

[dependencies.egui_plot]
workspace = true

[dependencies.env_logger]
workspace = true
features = ["auto-color", "humantime"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "custom_plot_manipulation"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[package]
name = "legend_sort"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["hacknus <l_stoeckli@bluewin.ch>"]
publish = false

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.license]
workspace = true

[package.rust-version]
workspace = true

[dependencies.eframe]
workspace = true
features = ["default"]

[dependencies.egui_plot]
workspace = true

[dependencies.env_logger]
workspace = true
features = ["auto-color", "humantime"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "legend_sort"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[package]
name = "save_plot"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["hacknus <l_stoeckli@bluewin.ch>"]
publish = false

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.license]
workspace = true

[package.rust-version]
workspace = true

[dependencies]
rfd = "0.15.1"
sccache = "0.10.0"

[dependencies.eframe]
workspace = true
features = ["default"]

[dependencies.egui_plot]
workspace = true

[dependencies.env_logger]
workspace = true
features = ["auto-color", "humantime"]

[dependencies.image]
workspace = true
features = ["png"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "save_plot"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

skeleton.config_file:
# clipboard api is still unstable, so web-sys requires the below flag to be passed for copy (ctrl + c) to work
# https://rustwasm.github.io/docs/wasm-bindgen/web-sys/unstable-apis.html
# check status at https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Clipboard#browser_compatibility
# we don't use `[build]` because of rust analyzer's build cache invalidation https://github.com/emilk/eframe_template/issues/93
[target.wasm32-unknown-unknown]
rustflags = ["--cfg=web_sys_unstable_apis"]
